description: Leyi iproject eyokwenelisa amalunga eGRM ukuthi ezilobele amabhuku angcwele ngolimi lwabo. Leyi android app iyakupha umzila munye ngamunye ukuthi umuntu azilobele ngolwimi lakhe. Imizila yonke oyithumeleyo iyahlanganisa uma abantu belokhe bethumela size sakhe ibhuku elipheleleyo.

name: solutions
description: Kanda kuri Link  maze utunge application yo kwiga amatageko y'umuhanda muri smart phone yawe     Application ikoranye ubuhanga, yagenewe kwigisha abantu  amategeko yumuhanda. Muri iyi app, twibanze kugukemura ikibazo kimwe, kugabanya igihe umuntu ata arimo ashakisha ibyo yiga, ndetse nigihe umuntu ata abyiga.  Smart phone turayihorana,turayigendana, nyamamara, ntiwagendana igazeti munzira! Tekereza igihe umara utegereje imodoka, igihe umara uri kurugendo nikindi gihe ubona kigupfiriye ubusa! Icyo gihe ntikikigupfiriye ubusa kuko uzacyifashisha ukora imyitozo muburyo bugezweho wifashishije application yacu.  Icyiza cyayo ntikenera internet ,ngo ube wakenera andi mafaranga, wowe yibikeho bibe birangiye! Kandi nuyikorersha tukwijejeko uzabona  permit yo gutwara imodoka nk umuntu usobanukiwe Ntakizamini kizagutsinda. Iyi  app irihagije muzasamgamo ibindi byinshi tutarondoye . Icyo twizeye 100% nuko kunyurwa byo muzanyurwa.   Enjoy  your app
